svg.text: 2019: Paper published in 48th “Studies in Chinese Literature”, National Taiwan University
2019: Won the 45th Youth Literary Award for Merit, HKU & CUHK
2017: Translate book: Stephen A. Thomas’ “Data Visualization with JavaScript”
2016: Create “UFO Animate, A CSS Animation Tool”
2011 - 2014: UI Development for Tencent Weibo, Tencent Online Media Group
2024: “The World Is As Beautiful as You”, Poems, Published in Hong Kong.
2025: “When the Leeves Break”, Novel, Translated Work, Nanjing: “Translations”
